<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Your Message</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #28a745;
        }

        .content {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Thank You for Your Message!</h1>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
                <p>Thank you for reaching out to the author. The author have received your message and the author will
                    review it shortly.
                </p>
                    <p><strong>Your Details:</strong></p>
                    <% if (blogSlug) { %>
                        <p><strong>Blog Slug:</strong>
                            <%= blogSlug %>
                        </p>
                        <% } %>
                            <p><strong>Email:</strong>
                                <%= email %>
                            </p>
                            <p><strong>Subject:</strong>
                                <%= subject %>
                            </p>
                            <p><strong>Message:</strong></p>
                            <p>
                                <%= message %>
                            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
                <p>If you have any immediate questions or concerns, please feel free to reply to <%= authorEmail %>.</p>
                <p>Best regards,<br><%= authorName %></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>